Yasmine Belmadi https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yasmine_Belmadi 0 Yasmine Belmadi (26 January 1976 – 18 July 2009) was a French actor of Algerian parents. He appeared in 13 films, and had completed his final role, in a television production, the day before his death.
